name: Glitchcraft #1: Solve et Coagula (Gateskeeper)
description: A hysterical historical moment, captured on camera. A glitched-out, frozen TV screen portrays a humanoid figure made up of coagulated pixels, accompanied by the headline "Bill Gates on solutions for saving the planet (and what we can learn from last week's storm in Texas)" as well as a marquee of distorted, unearthly scripture. By The Ungoogleable Michaelangelo, IG: void_denizen
